                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6244" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0957</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9609 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“千山”鸟飞绝：千山药机的财务舞弊之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Qianshan&quot; Birds Fly Away: The Road to Financial Fraud of Chinasun</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邹高峰，郭晴，冯勇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南千山制药机械股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">千山药机；财务造假；虚构收入；舞弊识别；退市</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chinasun Pharmachem；Financial Fraud; Fictitious Revenue; Fraud Identification; Delisting</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">千山药机是一家制药专用设备制造企业，2011年5月在创业板登陆，曾被认为是最具发展前景的明星概念股。然而，公司的发展却逐渐偏航，股价跌跌不休，报表频频难产，直到2020年7月靴子才终于落地——公司被查实重大财务造假，被深交所要求股票终止上市，再也不得重新上市，千山药机从此告别资本市场。本案例以千山药机在经营发展过程中的重大财务造假事件的前因后果为主线，详细介绍了企业走向财务造假之路的背景，财务舞弊所采用的手段，以及审计师前期的疏忽与后期的周旋，旨在帮助学生了解上市公司的财务造假的动因，掌握识别与应对企业舞弊风险的方法，学习相关的实质性审计程序，以提升其专业胜任能力与职业怀疑意识，建立风险导向审计的思维逻辑，为今后的实践提供经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Chinasun Pharmachem is a pharmaceutical special equipment manufacturer, which landed on the GEM in May 2011 and was once considered the most promising star concept stock. However, the development of the company gradually yawning, the stock price fell, the report frequently difficult to produce, until July 2020 boots finally landed - the company was found to be a major financial fraud, was required by the Shenzhen Stock Exchange to terminate the stock listing, never to be re-listed, Chinasun Pharmachem from the capital market farewell. This case focuses on the causes and consequences of a major financial fraud in the course of the business development of Chinasun Pharmachem, and introduces in detail the background of the enterprise towards the path of financial fraud, the means used for financial fraud, and the auditor&#39;s negligence in the early stage and the circumstance in the later stage, aiming to help students understand the motives of financial fraud in listed companies, master the methods of identifying and responding to the risks of corporate fraud, and learn the relevant substantive audit procedures to enhance their professional competence and awareness of professional skepticism, establish the thinking logic of risk-based auditing, and provide experience for future practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级审计理论与实务》、《高级财务会计理论与实务》、《会计案例研究与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">舞弊三角形理论；注册会计师应对舞弊风险的审计方法与审计程序介绍；主营业务收入的实质性审计程序；注册会计师接受的审计初步业务活动与风险评估程序</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
